Tinkaton (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0958: Tinkatuff
Pokémon
#0960: Wiglett →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Tinkaton (TCG Pocket).

Tinkaton has been featured on 5 different cards since it debuted in the Paldea Evolved expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Tinkaton cards are normally Psychic-type or Metal-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Tinkaton

Tinkaton
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
